title: Intervention S03E05 - Dillon
description:
Dillon is one sad story. Despite a big, loving family, he's always found himself immersed in trouble. From stealing cars in high school to his current crystal meth addiction, he never seems to be able to crawl out of the hole. Coupled with his bipolar disorder - a mental condition for which he refuses to take medication for - he is a loose cannon. A heartbreaking intervention is followed by an even more heartbreaking conclusion. Spoiler alert: http://www.koco.com/Standoff-Suspect-Featured-On-A-E-s-Intervention/10737684
Season 3, Episode 6 of Intervention, Dillon.
